ma is about the life of a group of Hong Kong police officers and cadets inside and outside of work.\n\nA direct sequel, E.U. was produced and airred in 2009 continued with Ron Ng and Sammul Chan, alongside Michael Miu, Kathy Chow, Elanne Kwong, and Michael Tse.","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"3514","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2023-11-04T14:51:43.000Z","cast":["Trần Kiện Phong","Ngô Trác Hy","Joey Yung Jo-Yee","Đào Đại Vũ","Quách Thiện Ni","Kate Tsui Tsz-Shan","Tiền Gia Lạc","Lưu Gia Huy","Huệ Anh Hồng","Florence Kwok Siu-Wan","La Quán Lan","Trần Quốc Bang","Lý Thi Hoa","Dương Thiến Nghiêu","Fiona Sit Hoi-Kei"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Trần Kiện Phong","name_vi":"Trần Kiện Phong","name_original":"Sammul Chan","tmdb_id":1222624,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/emuTVeFoAewmALU0EVzpDxk3dEn.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1222624"},{"name":"Ngô Trác Hy","name_vi":"Ngô Trác Hy","name_original":"Ron Ng Cheuk-Hai","tmdb_id":1222249,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rhT0EL5LYYLZIyS3Aax6MakEE9e.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1222249"},{"name":"Joey Yung Jo-Yee","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Joey Yung Jo-Yee","tmdb_id":134991,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1Tmyfs4TZCHhwebzH33Wlz09G9L.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/134991"},{"name":"Đào Đại Vũ","name_vi":"Đào Đại Vũ","name_original":"Michael Tao Tai-Yu","tmdb_id":1169789,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/njBYOEYCuf8s5Bhe2M51dzIS5hK.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1169789"},{"name":"Quách Thiện Ni","name_vi":"Quách Thiện Ni","name_original":"Sonija Kwok Sin-Nae","tmdb_id":1223071,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/UPKGvicMcTMLHZ0vuc49sV0BoG.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1223071"},{"name":"Kate Tsui Tsz-Shan","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kate Tsui Tsz-Shan","tmdb_id":131256,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/d1YkPN0x4o46Jz7ws5WowWgOoW8.jpg